children.name: verify that user should Build You Own Computer and add them to cart successfully

When I click on computer tab
And I click on Desktop link
And I click on Bulit your own computer
And I select  "2.2 GHz Intel Pentium Dual-Core E2200" from processor
And I select "2 GB" from RAM
And I select "320 GB" from Harddrive
And I select "Vista Home [+$50.00]" from operating system
And I select "Microsoft Office [+$50.00]" from software
And I click on add to cart button
Then I can see the message proudct has been added to your shopping cart
